/div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="container striped-bg circle-boxes"><div class="column span4 first"><div class="text-center"><img class="img-circle" data-src="holder.js/140x140" alt="140x140" style="width: 180px; height: 180px;" src="/library/2014/Bordar-a-forsidu/-350x290-Bordar-litlir/lattuitherheyra-_hringur - Copy (1).jpg" /></div><p style="text-align: center;"><span>
